<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Construction Report - {{ decision.address }}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; padding: 20px; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
        th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left; }
        th { background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>시공사용 건축 보고서</h1>
    <p><strong>대상지:</strong> {{ decision.address }}</p>
    
    <h2>건축 가능 규모</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>항목</th><th>값</th></tr>
        <tr><td>최대 건축면적</td><td>{{ decision.scale.max_building_area | format_area }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>최대 연면적</td><td>{{ decision.scale.max_floor_area | format_area }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>예상 세대수</td><td>{{ decision.scale.estimated_units }}세대</td></tr>
        <tr><td>예상 층수</td><td>{{ decision.scale.total_floors }}층</td></tr>
    </table>
    
    <h2>공사비 추정</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>항목</th><th>금액</th></tr>
        <tr><td>건축 공사비</td><td>{{ decision.capex.construction_cost | format_currency }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>설계 감리비</td><td>{{ decision.capex.design_supervision | format_currency }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>예비비</td><td>{{ decision.capex.contingency | format_currency }}</td></tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
